  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Award winning cuisine and restaurant service.</p>
<p>Breakfast is an extensive hot and cold buffet with display chef.</p>
<p>Dinner is a four course meal with four choices of main dish plus salad buffet and cheese selection.</p>
<p>Various weekly themed buffets.</p>
<p>Special Christmas and New Year gala dinners included (formal dress).</p>
<p>Smart casual wear required at all meal times including breakfast.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
