  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Edelweiss &amp; Gurgl is <a rel="noopener" data-udi="umb://document/6e448fc9d4404ad59b2952657506e71d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6e448fc9d4404ad59b2952657506e71d}" target="_blank" title="Hotel Edelweiss &amp; Gurgl">Obergurgl’s</a> stand out hotel and the first thing you will notice is the size of the hotel, which stands out even in these beautiful settings.</p>
<h2>Ski-in, ski-out</h2>
<p>You couldn't find a more ideal location, with ski-in, ski-out access and Hohe Mut and Rosskar lifts located directly outside the hotel. The hotel is also in the centre of town so you don't have to travel far to see what Obergurgl has to offer.</p>
<h2>Spa</h2>
<p>Try out the hotel's Glacier Spa which has indoor and outdoor pools with views across the slopes, Finnish sauna, whirlpool, steam room, cold grotto, wading pool and gym. Treat yourself to a massage or beauty treatment, bookable locally. </p>
<h2>Bars &amp; lounges</h2>
<p>The après ski ice bar with large sun terrace is always lively and a popular spot for après being located directly next to the lifts. If you fancy something more sophisticated, the hotel's bar &amp; lounge is a great space to relax with a cocktail or glass of wine.</p>
<h3>Exclusive to Inghams</h3>
<p>As a ski specialist tour operator we carefully select the very best accommodation in our resorts and package them with flights and transfers, so that you can make the most of your holiday. We have an exclusive agreement with Hotel Edelweiss &amp; Gurgl the only UK tour operator to package and sell holidays here - all the more reason to book with Inghams today!</p>]]></description>
