  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Spiegelkogel </strong>Austrian twins room are around 20m² and have south facing balconies.</p>
<p><strong>Brunnenkogel</strong> Austrian twin rooms are around 24m² and have north facing balconies.</p>
<p><strong>Zuckerhüttl </strong>Austrian twin rooms can sleep up to three using a single sofa bed. These rooms are around 28m² and have north facing balconies.</p>
<p><strong>Brunnenkogel Suites </strong>offer the most space at 45m² and are good for families. Making use of the double sofa bed they are suitable for three adults or two adults and two children. These suites also have a north facing balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Single rooms </strong>are around 16m² and have a south facing balcony.</p>
